# [[Julio Ramón Ribeyro]], ''Alienation'' # [[Luis Loayza]], ''Cold Afternoons'' # [[Fernando Ampuero]], ''Bad Manners'' # [[Jorge Eduardo Benavides]], ''It Doesn't Have to Be This Way'' # [[Guillermo Niño de Guzmán]], ''No More Than A Shadow'' # [[Alonso Cueto]], ''The Love Artist '' # [[Gunter Silva Passuni]], ''Homesick'' # [[Ricardo Sumalavia]], ''The Offering''
César Ferreira describes the anthology as "a welcome and timely contribution that makes available some of the best short fiction to come out of Peru in recent decades."<ref>[[César Ferreira]], January 2015, “[http://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/2015/january/beings-contemporary-peruvian-short-stories Beings Contemporary Peruvian Short Stories]”. ''[[World Literature Today]]'' (accessed 5 February 2016)</ref>
